{"id":246344,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-上海虹桥机场附近居民抗议飞机噪音（组/","date":"2012-08-10T08:15:52Z","modified":"2012-08-10T08:15:52Z","title":"维权网 | 上海虹桥机场附近居民抗议飞机噪音（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，上海虹桥机场</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>名居民聚集在该机场大厅内，将抗议横幅和机场噪音扰民的材料摊在地板上，向旅客展示。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与抗议的居民展示着“为了基本的生存，我们必须依法离开死亡地带”的横幅；还有“新中国的人间地狱”、“政府漠视人权”的贴画；特别引人注目的是“政府漠视人权”、“抗议侵犯人权”等传单。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，上海虹桥机场附近居民不堪飞机噪音污染，多次向有关部门反映，至今没有得到解决。于是，该地区居民才到机场大厅的现场轮流抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bbS5b5aD1ag/UCTAz324GfI/AAAAAAAALLQ/ifUnfvIMnRA/s1600/DSCN0761.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bbS5b5aD1ag/UCTAz324GfI/AAAAAAAALLQ/ifUnfvIMnRA/s320/DSCN0761.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SwpgXQpkLvs/UCTA3CReGSI/AAAAAAAALLY/9kLdvuXGQFk/s1600/DSCN0762.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-SwpgXQpkLvs/UCTA3CReGSI/AAAAAAAALLY/9kLdvuXGQFk/s320/DSCN0762.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UfjjXBACdG0/UCTA6J67YeI/AAAAAAAALLg/zqTOhbYTAFA/s1600/DSCN0763.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UfjjXBACdG0/UCTA6J67YeI/AAAAAAAALLg/zqTOhbYTAFA/s320/DSCN0763.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_paAot80ooY/UCTA9Ey8tDI/AAAAAAAALLo/A70a_LGDyCI/s1600/DSCN0766.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://